cdata.name: Zeusshield
cdata.desc:
Zeusshield is a platform that will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to provide insurance services aiming to have a different business model compared to thetraditional model used by insurance companies.

Zeusshield Coin (ZSC) is an ERC-20 token that will be used to establishan insurance capital pool, in order to,improve thecash flows from insurance contracts.
